Changelog
=========

v0.2.5 (2014-11-27)
-------------------

-  Changelog. [jenkins]

v0.2.4 (2014-11-27)
-------------------

- Fix iscroll imports. [Teemu Laukka]

v0.2.3 (2014-11-25)
-------------------

- Add EditBackgroundModal. [tanelih]

- Add RemoveBoardModal. [tanelih]

- Replace workspace modals with refactored ones. [tanelih]

- Add Create and Remove modals for boards. [tanelih]

- Add a 'EditBoardModal' service, based on 'Modal' service. Very basic
  styles for 'Modal'. [tanelih]

- Add a 'modal' service. [tanelih]

- Use 'limitTo' filter, instead of separate 'truncate'. [tanelih]

v0.2.2 (2014-11-19)
-------------------

- Refactor most 'bower_components' into 'node_modules'. [tanelih]

  Remove 'text-angular', 'angular-truncate', 'ng-sanitize'. Remove
  'adaptive-speech' because it is a joke. Replace 'underscore' with
  'lodash'.

